These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
House: farmhouse, tower, victorian, modern, townhouse
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, family, satire, western, zombie
There are 5 different nationalities: british, chinese, egyptian, malaysian, turkish
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: orchid, daisy, rose, dahlia, balloon-flower
 1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the tower house##1
 3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 4. the victorian house is the victorian house##1
 5. the person who growsorchid is the person watching crime movies##1
 6. the townhouse house is on the left of the victorian house##1
 7. the british is on the left of the egyptian##1
 8. the modern house is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 9. the modern house is on the far right##1
10. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
11. the townhouse house is between the chinese and the person watching zombie movies##2
12. the malaysian is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
13. the turkish is on the right of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| House      | farmhouse        | tower | townhouse     | victorian   | modern |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | family      | western | zombie   | crime    |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | chinese     | british | egyptian | turkish  |
| Flower           | daisy | rose      | balloon-flower     | dahlia   | orchid     |

