.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, old-henry, havana, davidoff, dannemann
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, d&b, disco, r&b, techno
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, indian, polish, spanish
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, may, june, march, july
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of techno is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 3. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 4. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is between the chinese and the fan of techno##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is the old-henry-smoker##1
 7. the fan of country is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 8. the indian is the fan of r&b##1
 9. the indian is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
10. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
11. the indian is the havana-smoker##1
12. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Cigar         | davidoff | montecristo | dannemann    | old-henry  | havana    |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | d&b       | disco      | country | r&b        |
| Nationality   | spanish   | dutch     | chinese    | polish  | indian     |
| Birthday     | june    | may | july | march | february |

