.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: tulip, zinnia, bellflower, aconite, daffodil
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, gospel, metal, pop, reggae
The people use 5 different means of transport: ship, tram, car, train, helicopter
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is the fan of gospel##1
 2. the person driving the train is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of pop is in the middle##1
 4. the person who growstulip is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 7. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 8. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 9. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
10. the person driving the ship is the person who growsaconite##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
13. the person driving the helicopter is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | collecting | singing     | puzzles   | filmmaking   | rock-climbing |
| Flower   | daffodil  | zinnia | tulip | aconite | bellflower        |
| Music-Genre   | metal      | gospel      | pop       | reggae       | ambient       |
| Transport         | tram | helicopter  | train    | ship    | car        |

