.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
There 5 different types of food: artichoke, onion, papaya, tomato, watermelon
5 different pets are kept: horse, rat, goat, fish, bird
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, bongani, alhambra, chaman, montecristo
There are 5 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, japanese, pakistani
 1. the egyptian is on the far left##1
 2. the owner of the horse is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
 3. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
 4. the pakistani is between the chaman-smoker and the person eating tomato##2
 5. the person eating onion is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 6. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the indonesian##1
 7. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 8. the owner of the bird is the bongani-smoker##1
 9. the montecristo-smoker is in the middle##1
10. the chaman-smoker is the british##1
11. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
12. the british is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
13. the bongani-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Food          | watermelon  | papaya     | tomato   | onion     | artichoke |
| Pet         | bird | horse    | goat  | fish | rat   |
| Cigar   | bongani        | ritmeester    | montecristo     | alhambra     | chaman    |
| Nationality   | egyptian    | indonesian | japanese | pakistani | british   |

