.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice, lemonade, milk, mirinda
There 5 different types of food: apricot, broccoli, lettuce, orange, watermelon
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, quad-bike, snowmobile, skateboard, bus
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, november, april, february, march
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 2. the person eating orange is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person eating apricot##2
 5. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
11. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
12. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
13. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Beverage   | milk       | mirinda       | almond-milk   | lemonade      | juice    |
| Food       | watermelon | orange        | apricot       | lettuce       | broccoli |
| Transport        | bus     | quad-bike        | skateboard | boat        | snowmobile  |
| Birthday      | february | april | june      | march | november  |

