 1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 3. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 6. the person driving the ship is between the person watching zombie movies and the person who's sport is baseball##2
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the owner of the frog##1
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the person who's sport is baseball##2
12. the person driving the van is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
13. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
