 3. the owner of the rat is the person playing chess##1
 4. the owner of the horse is between the person eating apricot and the egyptian##2
 5. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 6. the person eating avocado is in the middle##1
 7. the turkish is on the right of the colombian##1
 8. the mexican is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the pony is the turkish##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
11. the owner of the pony is on the right of the colombian##1
12. the owner of the dog is the person eating cabbage##1
13. the owner of the horse is on the left of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
