There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, juice, mirinda, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, september, october, march, august
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, golf, handball, sailing
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, swisher, bluemaster, alhambra, tiparillo
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is between the swisher-smoker and the person who's sport is cricket##2
 2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
 7. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
11. the bluemaster-smoker is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's birthday is in october##2
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
13. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | juice       | mirinda    | soy-milk | iced-tea  | 7up        |
| Birthday       | august | december | october  | march | september    |
| Sport       | golf        | handball   | cricket  | sailing   | basketball |
| Cigar   | alhambra       | bluemaster      | tiparillo      | davidoff | swisher  |

