.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: quad-bike, airplane, bus, train, boat
The people have 5 different jobs:  bartender, engineer, entrepreneur, fisherman, pilot
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, crime, fantasy, scientific
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, havana, dannemann, ritmeester, chaman
 1. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the fisherman is between the person watching crime movies and the entrepreneur##2
 3. the person driving the train is the fisherman##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person driving the train is between the pilot and the havana-smoker##2
 7. the ritmeester-smoker is the person driving the bus##1
 8. the person driving the quad-bike is the dannemann-smoker##1
 9. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the pilot##1
10. the bartender is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the entrepreneur is the person watching animation movies##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
13. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Transport      | quad-bike      | airplane         | train      | bus | boat     |
| Job           | engineer | entrepreneur | fisherman | pilot    | bartender  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | animation    | adventure | crime    | scientific |
| Cigar   | dannemann  | havana        | oliveros   | ritmeester    | chaman     |

