.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: bellflower, tulip, iris, marigold, azalea
There are 5 different nationalities: american, brazilian, dutch, egyptian, indonesian
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: fantasy, satire, drama, sports, animation
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, car, helicopter, jet-ski, ship
 1. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the egyptian is on the left of the brazilian##1
 3. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching satire movies is between the american and the person watching fantasy movies##2
 6. the american is on the far left##1
 7. the person who growsiris is between the person driving the airplane and the person who growsazalea##2
 8. the person who growstulip is between the person who growsmarigold and the person who growsbellflower##2
 9. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
10. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Flower         | azalea  | iris | marigold   | tulip      | bellflower |
| Nationality   | american   | egyptian    | brazilian | indonesian | dutch      |
| Movie-Genre           | drama | satire    | fantasy       | sports     | animation      |
| Transport     | helicopter | ship        | airplane  | car        | jet-ski    |

