.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, hiking, reading, berlin-climbing, skydiving
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, fantasy, martial-arts, musical, thriller
City: rome, edinburgh, hamburg, london, berlin
5 different pets are kept: bird, goldfish, ferret, hedgehog, hamster
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person watching thriller movies is between the owner of the hedgehog and the person traveling to berlin##2
 3. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the person watching thriller movies is the person traveling to rome##1
 5. the person traveling to rome is between the owner of the hamster and the person traveling to hamburg##2
 6. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person traveling to london##1
 8. the person who's hobby is berlin-climbing is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 9. the owner of the bird is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
10. the person who's hobby is berlin-climbing is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | reading    | skydiving  | hiking  | cooking      | berlin-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | thriller   | musical | martial-arts | documentary   |
| City   | hamburg | rome    | berlin    | london       | edinburgh         |
| Pet   | hedgehog  | goldfish | hamster    | ferret     | bird      |

 